%% OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code + PKCE — the correct flow for web/mobile/SPA
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant C as Client app
    participant A as Auth server
    participant R as Resource API
    U->>C: Click "log in"
    C->>A: Authorization request + PKCE challenge
    A->>U: Login + consent
    U->>A: Approve
    A->>C: Authorization code
    C->>A: Code + PKCE verifier
    A->>C: Access token (short) + refresh token
    C->>R: Request + access token
    R->>C: Protected resource
    Note over C,A: On expiry, exchange the refresh token for a new access token
